    <h3>Obverse</h3>
    
        <p>Green on polychrome, in chalcography and offset.<br />
On the right, in a circle, the effigy of the Republic looking to the left (in green background).</p>
        
        <p>
        <strong>Script:</strong>
        Latin    </p>
        
        <p>
        <strong>Lettering:</strong>
        <br />        <span id="obverse_lettering" class="lettering">BANCO CENTRAL DO BRASIL 1<br />
1 UM <br />
CRUZEIRO<br />
UM<br />
PRESIDENTE<br />
CONSELHO MONETÁRIO<br />
PRESIDENTE<br />
BANCO CENTRAL</span>
    </p>
            
        
        <p>
        <strong>Translation:</strong>
        <br />        Brazilian Central Bank 1<br />
One Cruzeiro<br />
President Monetary Council<br />
President Central Bank    </p>
        
        <p>
        <strong>Engraver:</strong>
        <a href="https://en.numista.com/catalogue/artist.php?id=3588">Benedicto Ribeiro</a>    </p>
        
        <p>
        <strong>Designer:</strong>
        <a href="https://en.numista.com/catalogue/artist.php?id=3074">Aloísio Sérgio Barbosa de Magalhães</a>    </p>
    
    <h3>Reverse</h3>
    
        <p>On the left, on green medallion, project of the building of the Amortization Box (in green background).</p>
        
        <p>
        <strong>Script:</strong>
        Latin    </p>
        
        <p>
        <strong>Lettering:</strong>
        <br />        <span id="reverse_lettering" class="lettering">1 BANCO CENTRAL DO BRASIL<br />
1<br />
1 UM CRUZEIRO UM<br />
CASA DA MOEDA DO BRASIL</span>
    </p>
            
        
        <p>
        <strong>Translation:</strong>
        <br />        1 Central Bank of Brazil<br />
One Cruzeiro<br />
Brazilian Mint    </p>
        
        <p>
        <strong>Engraver:</strong>
        <a href="https://en.numista.com/catalogue/artist.php?id=3588">Benedicto Ribeiro</a>    </p>
        
        <p>
        <strong>Designer:</strong>
        <a href="https://en.numista.com/catalogue/artist.php?id=3074">Aloísio Sérgio Barbosa de Magalhães</a>    </p>
    

    <h3>Watermark</h3>
    
